Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.14,0:24:19.98,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.98,0:24:21.60,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}你是那么地不可取代
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.60,0:24:24.56,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}因为一直陪伴在我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.73,0:24:27.98,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}你相信无可匹敌的爱吗
